H3.text: Who was the first emperor of Rome. Agustus

A4.text: Augustus was the founder of the Roman Empire, who reigned as the first Roman emperor from 27 BC until his death in AD 14.

A5.text: Octavian was named in Caesar's will as his primary heir after the assassination of Julius Caesar in 44 BC.
